euters.com/world/us/us-lawmakers-call-add-chinas-catl-gotion-import-ban-list-wsj-reports-2024-06-07/</link><description>据《华尔街日报》报道，一群共和党议员表示，中国电池公司宁德时代和国轩高科应立即列入进口禁令名单，指控其供应链使用强迫劳动。</description><pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 06:28:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-lawmakers-call-add-chinas-catl-gotion-import-ban-list-wsj-reports-2024-06-07/</guid></item><item><title>战争中普京将目光投向东方</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/amid-war-putin-looks-east-russias-window-europe-2024-06-07/</link><description>与西方隔绝的俄罗斯在圣彼得堡举行的顶级投资论坛上向中国和沙特阿拉伯等大国以及津巴布韦和阿富汗等长期前景推销其2万亿美元的经济。该论坛是沙皇建立的，作为通往欧洲的窗口。</description><pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 05:04:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/amid-war-putin-looks-east-russias-window-europe-2024-06-07/</guid></item><item><title>世界杯种子球队意味着中国队在关键的首尔预选赛中并不轻松</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/world-cup-seedings-mean-no-easy-ride-china-crunch-seoul-qualifier-2024-06-07/</link><description>尽管中国队已经晋级亚洲区预选赛第三轮，但在周二的世界杯预选赛中与韩国队相遇时，中国队不太可能轻松应对。</description><pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 04:25:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/world-cup-seedings-mean-no-easy-ride-china-crunch-seoul-qualifier-2024-06-07/</guid></item><item><title>中国出口稳步增长，但进口放缓影响前景</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-may-exports-pick-up-pace-top-forecast-boost-economic-recovery-2024-06-07/</link><description>5月份，中国的出口连续第二个月增长更快，这表明工厂主正在设法寻找海外买家，并在经济努力实现持久复苏之际为经济带来一些缓解。</description><pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 03:29:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-may-exports-pick-up-pace-top-forecast-boost-economic-recovery-2024-06-07/</guid></item><item><title>随着美国就业数据的临近，股市涨势暂停</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-06-07/</link><description>欧洲央行五年来首次降息后，周五全球股市徘徊在历史新高，交易员等待重要的美国月度就业数据，寻找美联储是否会很快跟进的线索。</description><pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 02:50:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-06-07/</guid></item><item><title>澳大利亚驻美国大使陆克文表示，台湾战争将改变世界</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/war-over-taiwan-would-change-world-says-australia-ambassador-us-kevin-rudd-2024-06-07/</link><description>澳大利亚驻美国大使陆克文在一次演讲中警告说，台湾战争的全球后果将与第二次世界大战的影响一样大，使世界“完全不同”。</description><pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 02:00:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/war-over-taiwan-would-change-world-says-australia-ambassador-us-kevin-rudd-2024-06-07/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾指责中国海警“野蛮”阻止医疗后送</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-accuses-chinese-coast-guard-barbaric-blocking-medical-evacuation-2024-06-07/</link><description>菲律宾海岸警卫队周五指责中国海岸警卫队阻止其在南海撤离一名生病的武装部队成员，称其行为“野蛮且不人道”。</description><pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 01:54:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-accuses-chinese-coast-guard-barbaric-blocking-medical-evacuation-2024-06-07/</guid></item><item><title>在非农就业测试之前，美元跌至八周低点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-hovers-near-8-week-low-payrolls-test-looms-2024-06-07/</link><description>周五，在重要的美国就业报告发布之前，美元徘徊在八周低点附近，该报告可能会让投资者更好地了解美联储何时可能开始降息。</description><pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 01:06:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-hovers-near-8-week-low-payrolls-test-looms-2024-06-07/</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯、中国与美国就联合国关于加沙停火计划的决议发生争执</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/russia-china-wrangle-with-us-over-un-resolution-gaza-ceasefire-plan-2024-06-07/</link><description>在联合国安理会拥有否决权的俄罗斯和中国周四对美国的一项决议草案表示担忧，该决议草案将支持总统乔·拜登概述的以色列和巴勒斯坦激进组织哈马斯之间停火的提议。</description><pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 00:51:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/russia-china-wrangle-with-us-over-un-resolution-gaza-ceasefire-plan-2024-06-07/</guid></item><item><title>中国警察局长与美国国土安全部部长讨论执法合作</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-police-chief-us-homeland-security-head-discuss-law-enforcement-cooperation-2024-06-06/</link><description>据中国官方媒体报道，中国公安部部长王晓红周四与美国国土安全部部长亚历杭德罗·马约卡斯进行视频通话，双方同意就禁毒和执法合作保持沟通。</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 23:59:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-police-chief-us-homeland-security-head-discuss-law-enforcement-cooperation-2024-06-06/</guid></item><item><title>特朗普建议对包括中国在内的非法移民国家征收关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/trump-suggests-tariffs-against-nations-including-china-over-illegal-immigration-2024-06-06/</link><description>共和党总统候选人唐纳德·特朗普周四表示，如果他赢得 11 月份的美国大选，他可能会对包括中国在内的不遏制无证移民从其领土流入美国的国家征收关税。</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 22:34:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/trump-suggests-tariffs-against-nations-including-china-over-illegal-immigration-2024-06-06/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：印度利率决定结束了疯狂的一周</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-06-06/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 21:48:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-06-06/</guid></item></channel></rss>